#

Honey Garlic Glazed Chicken Thighs

$15.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High-ProteinGluten-Free

Tags:

FastDinnerHigh-Protein

Description

Juicy chicken thighs coated in a sweet and savory honey garlic glaze, served with steamed vegetables for a balanced meal.

Ingredients

  • Chicken thighs: 4 pieces
  • Honey: 1/4 cup
  • Soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Ginger: 1 tsp, grated
  • Vegetable oil: 2 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Steamed broccoli: 2 cups
